\begin_layout Standard
A sequence of quantum jumps or photo-counts giving total counts 
\begin_inset Formula $\bm{c}=c_{1},\ldots c_{M}$
\end_inset

 is obtained.
 For times when there is no jump, 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\dot{\psi}_{c}=-i\hat{H}_{e}\psi_{c}.\label{eq:Lindblad_Master_Equation-1}
\end{equation}

