\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
These are linear functions that act on the quantum wave-function.
 New ones can readily be added.
 They reduce memory requirements, which is an advantage for large Hilbert
 spaces, where storing even sparse operators can require large quantities
 of memory.
 
\end_layout

