\begin_inset Formula $w$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
intermediate indices 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{i},$
\end_inset

 which are absent in the 
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

